6514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1173420/extras/bb297412468d1278ccc3d2a95d5fa530.mp4?t=1743596514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Create the character, equip it with essential utensils and attend lectures on different fields of magic. Within that, collect the experience points and collector’s cards representing all the witchcraft, equipment and creatures in the game.<br><br><br>DUEL &amp; BE THE BEST<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1173420/extras/717b14d0566b2df4aea777f43b16dbef.poster.avif?t=1743596514\" width=600 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1173420/extras/717b14d0566b2df4aea777f43b16dbef.webm?t=1743596514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1173420/extras/717b14d0566b2df4aea777f43b16dbef.mp4?t=1743596514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Duel with players from around the world in a very rarely seen card system. Be the best! Just through your activity and won duels collect the points for your fraction in the cyclically created and published rankings.<br><br><br>TASTE THE ADVENTURES<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1173420/extras/c56a58cf61031c7406b1f4c4506155f9.poster.avif?t=1743596514\" width=600 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1173420/extras/c56a58cf61031c7406b1f4c4506155f9.webm?t=1743596514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1173420/extras/c56a58cf61031c7406b1f4c4506155f9.mp4?t=1743596514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></vi